Hrm, using epics...they are still pretty decent items, and for the most part a lot easier/quicker to acquire than the NToV/Sleepers items...They may not be the 'best' anymore, but are a very nice stepping stone along the way.<br>
<br>
Hell you can get a rogue epic in a day...provided you've been a social rogue getting to 50...<br>
<br>
You need to build up the forces and equipment in a guild to be able to do progressively more difficult things....and epics are a pretty nice step along the way.<br>
<br>
