Gotta remember that the better weapons are pretty much for the melee classes. As a shaman the ratio on a weapon means little to me. The only weapon that comes close to my epic is something like a Staff of the Elder Claws or Sprinkler of the Spirits, both of which I'm not likely to see for several months if ever. It's the same for all the priest and caster classes pretty much; 90% of the better-than-epic weapons are for the melee classes.<br>
